      "content": "hey i'm working on this blog post called \"The Global Standard for Sophistication\" and i want to give advice on how to look and act professional when traveling or doing business abroad. basically like, what are the universal rules for being a sophisticated, high-class professional so people don't look unrefined? can u give me a list of some key etiquette rules for things like dining, dressing, and talking to people?",
